import React from 'react' import JsonData from './data.json' const ShowExams = () => { fetch("https://localhost:8443/onlineexam/control/UpdateExamMasterEvent", { method: "GET", headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json", Accept: "application/json", }, }).then((response)=>response.json()).catch((err)=>console.log(err)); const DisplayData=JsonData.map( (info)=>{ return( {info.id} {info.name} {info.city} {info.id} {info.name} {info.city} {info.id} {info.name} {info.city} {info.id} {info.name} {info.city} ) } ) return (
{DisplayData}
ExamId ExamName Description CreationDate ExpirationDate No of Questions Duration Minutes Pass Percentage Questions Randomized Answers Must Enable negative Mark Negative Mark value
) } export default ShowExams
